{"type":"message","id":"7cdb11ef","parentId":"ce1ff030","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:48:07.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否可以联网检索。我确实有 web_search 和 web_fetch 工具可以联网搜索和获取网页内容。\n\n根据我的工具能力：\n- web_search: 使用 Brave Search API 进行网页搜索\n- web_fetch: 获取和提取 URL 的可读内容（HTML → markdown/text）\n\n所以我确实可以联网检索。\n","thinkingSignature":"5ccd0c3aae2f36d68ca80097a6650d27d667ee5f82e5c7ff2582444abd3cd9a5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以！我有两个联网能力：\n\n1. **网页搜索** (`web_search`) - 用 Brave Search API 搜网页\n2. **获取网页内容** (`web_fetch`) - 抓取 URL 页面内容，提取为 Markdown\n\n不过需要联网的任务你直接说就行，我来帮你查~"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":14429,"output":129,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14750,"cost":{"input":0.0043286999999999996,"output":0.0001548,"cacheRead":0.000005759999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004489259999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774583281894,"responseId":"061530f2fee39b31532c5158c77c1b9f"}}
