{"type":"message","id":"78185014","parentId":"f2ac88ee","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:50:01.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是用户（小王子）在确认我的能力。让我总结一下我目前有的能力：\n\n1. 联网搜索 - web_search (Brave Search)\n2. 获取网页内容 - web_fetch\n3. 浏览器操控 - Agent Browser (Rust headless browser)\n\n用户确认了这些能力，我简洁回应即可。\n","thinkingSignature":"ff58314d7b448bde3212b0631b6bc84baac62427e7bf753e391e0b760cd62c7c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到！我目前的能力：\n\n- 🌐 **联网搜索** - Brave Search API\n- 📄 **抓取网页** - 获取 URL 内容转 Markdown\n- 🖥️ **浏览器操控** - Agent Browser（点击、填表、截图等）\n\n需要查什么直接说~"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2040,"output":125,"cacheRead":14592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16757,"cost":{"input":0.000612,"output":0.00015,"cacheRead":0.00043776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00119976}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774583393387,"responseId":"0615316107c0aa60a87450e212afa4b8"}}
